Ken Ryker https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ken_Ryker 0 Ken Ryker (born August 17, 1972) is the stage name of an American pornographic actor who appeared in gay, straight and bisexual pornographic movies. He was raised in Texas, but now resides in California. He is openly bisexual and had relationships with both men and women.
